          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">official <strong>On .NET Live</strong> stream</a
        >. We air weekly on Mondays from 11:00 AM US Central Time to noon. We're
        live on:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong
            ><a
              href="https://www.youtube.com/@dotnet"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">.NET ‚Äî YouTube</a
